# Exception: the balance-lock feature decision doc is reviewed content
# (no raw secrets / no PII / small markdown), check it in. Must use
# `/*` on the parent so the un-ignore below actually fires — git can't
# reinstate files whose parent directory is ignored outright.
!docs/research/BALANCE-LOCK.md
docs/architecture/*.docx
docs/*.pdf
CryptoPay_Receipt_*.pdf
*.tar.gz
docs/mpesa*.txt


